headline: Kraft Heinz Sees Cash Flow Surge Despite Stagnant Dividend
summary: The Kraft Heinz Company (NASDAQ:KHC) is one of the Best Dividend Leaders to Buy Now. The company was once a classic income stock known for regularly raising its dividend.
